1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:01:22,959 --> 00:01:23,760
My Lady,

3
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:26,560
her clothes show she died
a violent death.

4
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:27,879
You're unmarried.

5
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:28,640
You shouldn't look.

6
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:30,040
Don't stain your eyes.

7
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:31,159
Now that I've seen her,

8
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:33,560
I can't let her die in vain.

9
00:01:33,799 --> 00:01:34,439
But...

10
00:01:34,439 --> 00:01:35,359
Saving one life

11
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:36,760
is more important than anything.

12
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:37,879
Xiaotao, hurry.

13
00:01:38,079 --> 00:01:39,280
Take her to the manor for treatment.

14
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:40,560
Yes.

15
00:01:46,180 --> 00:01:50,180
=Episode 24=

16
00:01:50,319 --> 00:01:51,079
Lin Rulan,

17
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:52,920
do you have evidence?

18
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,040
Yes.

19
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:06,040
This is a common needle case.

20
00:02:06,319 --> 00:02:07,359
What proof is that?

21
00:02:07,719 --> 00:02:09,680
Everyone at Yanyu Embroidery House
knows it.

22
00:02:10,159 --> 00:02:11,680
This is Wu Lian's

23
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:13,080
personal needle case.

24
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,439
His name is carved on it.

25
00:02:15,919 --> 00:02:17,039
Magistrate Yu, do you remember

26
00:02:17,439 --> 00:02:20,280
the murder knife found
at Yanyu Embroidery House?

27
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,439
I remember.

28
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:24,800
The engraving matches that knife.

29
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:28,800
And the needles inside are
the ones Wu Lian always uses.

30
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:30,400
To embroider for the Princess Consort,

31
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:31,919
he must use these needles.

32
00:02:32,479 --> 00:02:36,039
Check the hem of her gown,
and you'll know.

33
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:39,719
Lin Rulan,

34
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:40,960
do you have additional evidence?

35
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,199
I have a witness.

36
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:43,840
The Princess Consort.

37
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,360
She knows

38
00:02:45,599 --> 00:02:47,840
Wu Lian was the last person
to see Ms. Meng Wan.

39
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,039
I can also prove

40
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:59,319
that when Ms. Meng Wan was buried,

41
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:02,039
she was clutching this needle case.

42
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:04,039
Your Highness,
I beg for a public trial of Wu Lian!

43
00:03:04,439 --> 00:03:05,639
Public trial!

44
00:03:05,719 --> 00:03:06,159
Public trial!

45
00:03:06,159 --> 00:03:07,039
Public trial!

46
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,360
Public trial!

47
00:03:08,439 --> 00:03:09,719
Public trial!

48
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,039
Public trial!

49
00:03:11,199 --> 00:03:12,319
Public trial!

50
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,840
Public trial!

51
00:03:14,719 --> 00:03:16,240
When Ms. Meng Wan was buried,

52
00:03:16,719 --> 00:03:19,159
Wu Lian's steward was watching
from the shadows.

53
00:03:19,479 --> 00:03:20,719
If he didn't kill her,

54
00:03:21,039 --> 00:03:22,439
why the guilt?

55
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,199
They forced me here!

56
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,639
I said nothing!

57
00:03:29,199 --> 00:03:31,919
The plaque that says
"Finest Embroidery House"

58
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,479
was bestowed by the Princess Consort.

59
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,560
If I had done anything wrong,

60
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:38,639
why would she have given it to me?

61
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,520
I gave it for your skill,

62
00:03:40,879 --> 00:03:42,560
not knowing your character.

63
00:03:47,879 --> 00:03:50,479
For three years, I waited for you alone.

64
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:53,199
All because I love beautiful gowns

65
00:03:53,479 --> 00:03:55,039
and admire Wu Lian's talent.

66
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,840
What is wrong with that?

67
00:03:58,759 --> 00:03:59,560
Lin Rulan,

68
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:02,639
do you have any other proof
that Wu Lian killed her?

69
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,599
Your Highness,

70
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,080
I have evidence.

71
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,039
Speak.

72
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,840
Before Ms. Meng Wan died,

73
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:08,960
she came to see me.

74
00:04:09,039 --> 00:04:09,840
Wu Lian

75
00:04:10,039 --> 00:04:14,280
had Ms. Meng Wan give me
a "Spring River" painting

76
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:18,079
to turn a blind eye to his unlawful acts

77
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:19,199
at the embroidery house.

78
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:21,079
I serve the court.

79
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:22,439
I serve the people.

80
00:04:22,439 --> 00:04:23,920
Not Wu Lian.

81
00:04:24,439 --> 00:04:26,120
Ms. Meng Wan also told me

82
00:04:26,439 --> 00:04:28,959
that if she ever met with misfortune,

83
00:04:29,079 --> 00:04:30,759
it would be Wu Lian's doing.

84
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:33,040
She knew too much.

85
00:04:33,399 --> 00:04:35,040
He would silence her.

86
00:04:36,079 --> 00:04:39,199
Lin Rulan and Meng Wan are
birds of a feather.

87
00:04:39,639 --> 00:04:42,399
My hand was injured by her.

88
00:04:42,639 --> 00:04:43,399
Your Highness, please see the truth.

89
00:04:44,279 --> 00:04:46,519
His hand was never hurt!

90
00:04:47,839 --> 00:04:48,519
Wang Lu.

91
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:48,879
Yes.

92
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,879
You faked a hand injury
to stay at the manor.

93
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:01,199
You lied to me!

94
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:03,839
Xiaoyi,

95
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:05,199
do you know?

96
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:08,519
Rulan has brought Wu Lian down.

97
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,399
She will avenge Meng Wan.

98
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:12,639
Meng Wan's death is now clear.

99
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,600
But you also accuse him
of defiling embroiderers.

100
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,040
Do you have proof?

101
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:17,439
Yes.

102
00:05:21,879 --> 00:05:23,199
I am the proof.

103
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:28,800
Three years ago,
I jumped off the wall for this.

104
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:32,600
You couldn't have me,
so you jumped,

105
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:35,600
and you had trouble with
your husband's family!

106
00:05:35,639 --> 00:05:36,800
What does that have to do with me?

107
00:05:36,879 --> 00:05:40,319
Then what about the list
in your fish tank?

108
00:05:40,319 --> 00:05:41,240
What does that mean?

109
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:46,920
You grab any list and slander me.

110
00:05:47,079 --> 00:05:50,480
The list was hidden
in a compartment in the tank.

111
00:05:51,519 --> 00:05:54,879
This thread is unique to
your embroidery house.

112
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:56,120
Present it.

113
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:57,439
Your Highness,

114
00:05:57,680 --> 00:06:00,560
this list concerns the chastity
of dozens of women.

115
00:06:01,079 --> 00:06:03,360
I request a female official
to re-examine it.

116
00:06:03,519 --> 00:06:04,879
I am a woman.

117
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:07,439
Let me see which women
Wu Lian violated.

118
00:06:07,839 --> 00:06:10,600
Who would dare to admit
they're on this list?

119
00:06:12,399 --> 00:06:14,920
Your Highness, do not threaten
these women with their reputations.

120
00:06:16,319 --> 00:06:18,560
I, Huang Jiaojiao, testify.

121
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:22,120
I studied at the embroidery house
two years ago.

122
00:06:22,319 --> 00:06:23,720
Wu Lian defiled me.

123
00:06:24,199 --> 00:06:25,519
After I married,

124
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,360
he threatened me withi this list,

125
00:06:27,639 --> 00:06:28,720
to keep me silent.

126
00:06:29,439 --> 00:06:32,240
If I let it slip, he'd kill me and
my husband's entire family.

127
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,959
My husband went to seek justice.

128
00:06:35,439 --> 00:06:36,519
Wu Lian had him killed.

129
00:06:38,519 --> 00:06:40,759
When Wu Lian defiled those
embroiderers,

130
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:43,160
he embroidered handkerchiefs
with the flower of that season

131
00:06:43,399 --> 00:06:44,480
to feed his desires.

132
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:46,920
Beast!

133
00:06:47,279 --> 00:06:48,160
It's him!

134
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:48,560
Xiaoyi!

135
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,199
It's him!

136
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,079
Xiaoyi!

137
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,120
Don't be afraid, Xiaoyi.

138
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:51,560
It's okay.

139
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,279
Wu Lian,

140
00:06:52,399 --> 00:06:53,720
what say you?

141
00:06:53,959 --> 00:06:54,759
Princess Consort,

142
00:06:55,399 --> 00:06:56,800
don't listen to these lies!

143
00:06:56,879 --> 00:06:57,959
They're in collusion!

144
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:58,839
Princess Consort,

145
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,439
kill them!

146
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:02,040
Kill them!

147
00:07:03,879 --> 00:07:06,959
Three years ago, when Lin Rulan
first told me,

148
00:07:07,639 --> 00:07:10,319
I couldn't believe such evil
existed in this world.

149
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:13,920
Wu Lian. It's a good thing

150
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:16,279
I had Lin Rulan impersonate me
to confront you.

151
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:17,560
If not,

152
00:07:18,279 --> 00:07:19,800
how long would your arrogance
have continued?

153
00:07:21,879 --> 00:07:24,439
Wenyue, right under your nose,

154
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,959
such an evil man ran wild for years.

155
00:07:27,439 --> 00:07:28,600
I may have indulged him,

156
00:07:29,439 --> 00:07:31,959
but I didn't know
he committed such crimes.

157
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,279
Princess Consort,

158
00:07:35,279 --> 00:07:37,199
you know what kind of person I am!

159
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,279
They...

160
00:07:40,279 --> 00:07:42,800
They begged to study at my house.

161
00:07:43,079 --> 00:07:45,160
They begged to learn my craft

162
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:47,079
so they could marry well.

163
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,120
These wretches...

164
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,639
They were all willing.

165
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,240
I grew up poor.

166
00:07:54,399 --> 00:07:56,040
I learned this craft.

167
00:07:56,319 --> 00:07:58,199
I've ruled Jinxiu City for years.

168
00:07:58,279 --> 00:07:59,560
People respect me.

169
00:08:00,439 --> 00:08:02,639
But I still have to be your dog,

170
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,600
pamper you, and flatter you.

171
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,480
I must stand above them all!

172
00:08:06,519 --> 00:08:07,279
Wu Lian,

173
00:08:07,439 --> 00:08:08,800
you are despicable!

174
00:08:09,319 --> 00:08:10,160
This has gone too far.

175
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,319
Confess your crimes!

176
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,800
Forgive me, Your Highness.

177
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,720
I failed to discipline him.

178
00:08:19,279 --> 00:08:20,920
I indulged the wicked to do harm.

179
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:23,439
Punish Wu Lian severely.

180
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:25,040
You wretches!

181
00:08:25,279 --> 00:08:26,360
You dare punish me?

182
00:08:27,879 --> 00:08:29,720
Look! Look!

183
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,319
Wu Lian!

184
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:32,320
What are you doing?

185
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:33,759
Let go!

186
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:35,440
Look!

187
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,840
Let go!

188
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:37,759
Look!

189
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:41,720
Who said

190
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:43,879
only I can embroider
the dancing phoenix?

191
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:45,240
Who said

192
00:08:45,879 --> 00:08:48,519
only I can preserve your beauty?

193
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,799
And who said

194
00:08:51,279 --> 00:08:52,360
that as long as you're here,

195
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:54,039
in Jinxiu City,

196
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:56,039
no one can touch me?

197
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,960
Seize Wu Lian!

198
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:58,279
Yes!

199
00:08:58,679 --> 00:08:59,559
Your Highness,

200
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:02,120
Her Highness only sought beauty.

201
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:04,360
Don't blame her.

202
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,639
No one can judge me!

203
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:31,519
No one in this world!

204
00:09:50,399 --> 00:09:51,840
Escort my wife back to the manor.

205
00:09:59,799 --> 00:10:00,519
Your Highness.

206
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,759
Is there anything else you wish to say?

207
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,440
I'm here.

208
00:10:21,639 --> 00:10:22,600
Speak freely.

209
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,559
I only wish for a just world.

210
00:10:25,399 --> 00:10:28,799
May innocent women no longer
be crushed by the powerful,

211
00:10:29,879 --> 00:10:31,600
no longer shamed by society.

212
00:10:33,399 --> 00:10:36,720
If all women had Rulan's courage,

213
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:39,080
evil would never triumph.

214
00:10:39,639 --> 00:10:40,399
Your Highness,

215
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:41,759
I hope that after today,

216
00:10:42,039 --> 00:10:45,519
the world will know
that a woman's honor lies in her heart,

217
00:10:45,639 --> 00:10:46,919
not in chains.

218
00:10:47,799 --> 00:10:50,080
Your Highness, do you swear?

219
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,799
From this day forward,

220
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,519
the women of Jinxiu City

221
00:10:54,679 --> 00:10:56,440
will not be judged by chastity,

222
00:10:56,799 --> 00:10:58,799
but by virtue.

223
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,240
Lin Rulan,

224
00:11:01,279 --> 00:11:02,440
what else do you wish for?

225
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:12,679
If someone had stood up back then,

226
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:14,919
perhaps all of this
would have been different.

227
00:11:15,279 --> 00:11:17,360
Women have great ambitions.

228
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,879
Heroes are not only men.

229
00:11:20,799 --> 00:11:22,240
The women of Jinxiu City,

230
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:26,080
with their delicate hands,
have upheld justice under heaven.

231
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,440
That is how we arrived at this moment,

232
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:30,039
this more satisfying

233
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,720
and complete resolution.

234
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,200
Crimes have been determined.

235
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:37,480
Victims shall not be forced
to face their accusers.

236
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:51,159
Good!

237
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:58,440
Good!

238
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:01,000
Your Highness is wise!

239
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,080
Good!

240
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:06,759
Get in!

241
00:12:38,580 --> 00:12:41,540
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

242
00:12:41,780 --> 00:12:43,980
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

243
00:12:43,980 --> 00:12:45,980
(Grave of Meng Wan)

244
00:12:45,980 --> 00:12:48,420
♪The past no longer binds♪

245
00:12:48,420 --> 00:12:49,260
(Grave of Feng Da)

246
00:12:49,260 --> 00:12:52,940
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

247
00:12:53,380 --> 00:12:57,500
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

248
00:12:58,340 --> 00:13:01,220
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

249
00:13:01,580 --> 00:13:03,580
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

250
00:13:03,580 --> 00:13:07,660
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

251
00:13:08,060 --> 00:13:10,260
♪For your faith that never broke♪

252
00:13:10,460 --> 00:13:14,580
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

253
00:13:15,460 --> 00:13:17,380
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

254
00:13:17,380 --> 00:13:21,620
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

255
00:13:22,820 --> 00:13:25,300
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

256
00:13:25,420 --> 00:13:28,060
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

257
00:13:28,060 --> 00:13:30,660
♪One thought turns into ash♪

258
00:13:31,620 --> 00:13:36,980
♪No future left to write♪

259
00:14:07,540 --> 00:14:10,500
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

260
00:14:10,740 --> 00:14:13,740
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

261
00:14:14,940 --> 00:14:17,700
♪The past no longer binds♪

262
