♪My heart still shines through dust♪

263
00:14:22,340 --> 00:14:26,460
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

264
00:14:27,300 --> 00:14:30,180
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

265
00:14:30,540 --> 00:14:32,540
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

266
00:14:32,540 --> 00:14:36,620
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

267
00:14:37,020 --> 00:14:39,220
♪For your faith that never broke♪

268
00:14:39,420 --> 00:14:43,540
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

269
00:14:44,420 --> 00:14:46,340
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

270
00:14:46,340 --> 00:14:50,580
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

271
00:14:51,780 --> 00:14:54,260
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

272
00:14:54,380 --> 00:14:57,020
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

273
00:14:57,020 --> 00:14:59,620
♪One thought turns into ash♪

274
00:15:00,580 --> 00:15:05,940
♪No future left to write♪

275
00:15:07,020 --> 00:15:08,820
♪If I never fall♪

276
00:15:08,860 --> 00:15:11,220
♪How could this waiting end♪

277
00:15:11,220 --> 00:15:12,580
♪If I bear no scars♪

278
00:15:12,580 --> 00:15:14,900
♪How could I challenge fate♪

279
00:15:14,900 --> 00:15:17,260
♪I knew there was no way back♪

280
00:15:17,260 --> 00:15:21,260
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

281
00:15:21,380 --> 00:15:23,500
♪For your faith that never broke♪

282
00:15:23,700 --> 00:15:27,660
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

283
00:15:28,620 --> 00:15:30,540
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

284
00:15:30,540 --> 00:15:34,940
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

285
00:15:36,020 --> 00:15:38,620
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

286
00:15:38,660 --> 00:15:41,220
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

287
00:15:41,220 --> 00:15:43,580
♪One thought turns into ash♪

288
00:15:44,700 --> 00:15:49,940
♪No future left to write♪

289
00:15:50,820 --> 00:15:53,220
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

290
00:15:54,500 --> 00:15:56,620
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

291
00:15:58,300 --> 00:16:00,500
♪If we meet again someday♪

292
00:16:00,940 --> 00:16:06,740
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
